  { question: 'Fashion browse specifics?', answer: 'Fit UGC, size guide, variant inventory — see fashion vertical guide.' },
  { question: 'B2B browse?', answer: 'Route high-MOQ browse to rep notification — not consumer browse discount.' },
  { question: 'Audit frequency?', answer: 'Quarterly; after catalog or popup offer changes.' },
