<p><strong>Capture coordination:</strong> Popup offer state prevents browse incentive stacking. Playbook fit: Email one proof-only if popup delivered. Failure mode: Double offer browse + popup. Operator test: Collision audit monthly.</p>
<p><strong>Analytics:</strong> Browse-to-cart rate, proof path revenue, holdout incrementality. Playbook fit: Separate reporting from cart recovery. Failure mode: Attributed browse revenue is actually cart recovery. Operator test: Distinct UTM/flow tags per playbook.</p>
